suggestions.title: Fix `lib/src/model/selection/noop_selection_model_impl.dart`.
suggestions.description:
Analysis of `lib/src/model/selection/noop_selection_model_impl.dart` reported 2 warnings, 1 hint:

line 20 col 31: Parameters can't override default values, this method overrides 'SelectionObservable.notifySelectionChange' where 'added' has a different value.

line 20 col 38: Parameters can't override default values, this method overrides 'SelectionObservable.notifySelectionChange' where 'removed' has a different value.

line 37 col 26: Avoid shadowing type parameters.

suggestions.description:
Create a short demo in the `example/` directory to show how to use this package.

Common filename patterns include `main.dart`, `example.dart`, and `angular_components.dart`. Packages with multiple examples should provide `example/README.md`.

For more information see the [pub package layout conventions](https://www.dartlang.org/tools/pub/package-layout#examples).
